
  Usage: mrblog <command>
     or: <blog action>

Commands (can be called anywhere):
    new                     : create a new post using timestamp as filename
    new <filename>          : create a new post using custom filename
    find                    : find a specific post and edit / rename / delete it
    publish                 : publish posts
    pic                     : picture posting helper
    content                 : open content folder
    sketchdump              : auto dump sketches to blog

Blog actions (need to be at blog site's directory) 
             (run "cd $MRBLOG_PATH" first):
    scripts/setup           : make local setups for blog
    npm run deploy          : deploy blog
